00:00:12.949 --> 00:00:16.262
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:24.301 --> 00:00:26.796
What are you going to cook for us today?
Carrot Fried Rice

00:00:31.862 --> 00:00:36.466
Ingredients required for Carrot Fried Rice

00:00:37.393 --> 00:00:50.767
Carrot, Raw Coconut, Green Chillies, Mustard Seeds, Cumin Seeds, Ginger Garlic Paste,
Capsicum, Rice, Coriander, Garam Masala, Cashew Nuts, Salt &amp; Ghee

00:01:06.974 --> 00:01:23.588
First heat two spoons of ghee in a pan, fry some cashew nuts in it &amp; keep them aside

00:01:34.846 --> 00:01:49.362
Now add some oil in the pan, add cumin seeds &amp; mustard seeds to it

00:01:57.682 --> 00:02:30.756
Add some sliced green chillies, 1/2 cup of grated carrot &amp; raw coconut
and fry them for a while

00:02:49.305 --> 00:03:11.251
Now add some capsicum slices, ginger garlic paste into the pan
&amp; fry it for a while

00:03:14.909 --> 00:03:46.563
Now add some boiled rice &amp; some salt to the pan
&amp; mix it well

00:03:49.585 --> 00:04:06.843
Add some garam masala to the pan &amp; mix it well

00:04:15.744 --> 00:04:27.664
Take the Carrot Fried Rice into a serving bowl,
garnish it with fried cashew nuts &amp; coriander leaves

